data.title: Maria Letizia “Madame Mère” Ramolino Buonaparte ...
data.meta_description: Daughter of Gian Girolamo Ramolino and Angela Maria Pietra-Santa Royalty. Born in 1750 in Ajaccio Corsica she marries Carlo Bonaparte at the of 14. Their second son Napoleon will become emperor of France and king of Italy and 3 of her other sons will become king. After Napoleons abdication she goes in exile in Italy...
